Token.Abstract: When a request for autoCompletion is received, a previous, unfinished one should be considered abandoned and the request can be cancelled.
Implement this method to provide auto-completion results for hashtags. This method will be called on the main thread.

Parameter.Name: hashtag
Parameter.Abstract: The hashtag (starting with #) to use to search for similar ones.

Parameter.Name: callback
Parameter.Abstract: Must be called at most once, on any queue, with the results of the hashtag autoCompletion to be shown.

Token.Abstract: Implement this method to provide auto-completion results for users. This method will be called on the main thread.

Parameter.Name: username
Parameter.Abstract: The username (not starting with @) to use to search for matching users.

Parameter.Name: callback
Parameter.Abstract: Must be called at most once, on any queue, with the results of the user autoCompletion to be shown.
